<h2>Add new animal</h2>

<p>This page is for staff to register an animal with the charity. Be as specific and descriptive as possible, as we will use your entry as a reference.</p>

<form action = "/shelter/animals" method = "post">

  <hr/><p>
  
    <label for="name">
      Enter animal name. 
    </label>

    <input id="name" name="name" type="text"/>
  
  </p><hr/>

  <p>
  
    <label for="type">
      Type of animal. Begin 'Exotic -' if the animal is a bird, reptile or invertebrate, or non-native to the UK, with the exception of common companion animals. 
    </label>
    
    <input id="type" name="type" type="text"/>
  
  </p><hr/>

  <p>
  
    <label for="admission_date">
      Date and time admitted: 
    </label>

    <input id="admission_date" name="admission_date" type="text"/>
  
  </p><hr/>

  <p>
  
    <label for="adoptable">
      Is the animal ready for adoption? Either way, describe the animal's health and temperament. 
    </label>

    <input id="adooptable" name="adoptable" type="text"/>
  
  </p><hr/>

  <input type="submit" value="Register animal"/>

</form>